scopecontent.p:
The records of this now defunct group include: press releases; correspondence and
                    proposals related to fundraising; public opinion polls on nuclear power;
                    materials related to various campaigns, including the ALMR (Advanced Light
                    Metals Reactor) and Ohio/Sacramento Municipal Utilities Department campaigns;
                    financial records; meeting minutes of the board of directors (on paper and on
                    audio cassette); PSAs and [promotional/educational] video and audio recordings
                    and slide presentations; cassette and video recordings of meetings and events;
                    press clippings; letters to the editors of various publications; media kits; and
                    SECC publications.
